          technologies. My deep understanding of both development areas allows
          me to deliver robust applications with exceptional user experiences.
        </p>
        <p>
          I have gained alot of experience from working with small teams and
          gained awards from my <a
            class="link"
            href="https://twitter.com/IPRC__Ngoma/status/1565622456269824001"
            >innovative projects</a
          >.
        </p>
        <h3>Skills</h3>
        <p>
          <span>figma</span><span>adobe XD</span><span>adobe illustrator</span
          ><span>inkscape</span><span>HTML/CSS</span><span>bootstrap</span><span
            >tailwindCSS</span
          ><span>Sass</span><span>javascript</span><span>typescript</span><span
            >reactjs</span
          ><span>redux</span><span>zustand</span><span>jest</span><span
            >nodejs</span
          ><span>express</span><span>nextjs</span><span>mocha</span><span
            >java</span
          ><span>modern PHP</span><span>c/c++</span><span>mysql</span><span
            >postgresql</span
          ><span>mongodb</span><span>docker</span><span>git</span><span
            >linux server</span
          >
        </p>
        <a href="/resume" class="btn">my resume / CV</a>
      </div>
      <Image
        class="image"
        src={profile}
        format="webp"
        width={200}
        height={250}
        alt="https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/103575700?v=4"
      />
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

<style lang="scss">
  section {
    min-height: 100dvh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }
  article {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: auto 25%;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    opacity: 1 !important;
  }
  a.link {
    text-decoration: underline;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .image {
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    width: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    mix-blend-mode: multiply;
    filter: contrast(100%) brightness(200%) invert(0);
    scale: 1.5;
    translate: 0 -25%;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 2em;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  span {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;

    &:hover::before {
      width: 100%;
      transform: translateX(100%);
    }

    &::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      width: 0;
      height: 100%;
      background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      transition: 1s;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 780px) {
    article {
      grid-template-columns: auto 20%;
    }
  }
  @media (max-width: 550px) {
    article {
      grid-template-columns: auto;
      justify-items: center;
    }

    img {
      width: 200px;
    }
  }
</style>
